{
  "stem": "8370.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The bread which was cut in four in Auschwitz now was cut in 12.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had really very poor food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Of course, this was already when the front moved more to the west, the parcels, food parcels, stopped.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we have to rely only on this, what we receive in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we were hungry day and night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember I had a dream in Heinkel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had a dream that I received from somebody a slice of bread with this beetroots marmalade on top.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was eating this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I waked up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I say, what a beautiful dream I had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Well, and on the 13th of April, '45, arrived 700 bombers from American bomber command, and bombed out the factory.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "From 4,500 people after-- after this bombardment-- daytime, about two o'clock-- they have done a roll call.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were 1,500 alive of prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why, at this very moment, say, three weeks before the end of the war, they bombed a concentration camp, knowing that there are prisoners inside, knowing that this production there was useless, really, because we never arrived to the front in time?",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We produced the Dornier planes, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But was far behind the schedule and never will be ready for going to the front.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, so it was a disaster there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then about on the 20, 20, a couple, one week later, we went a roll call.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In early morning, we started march, evacuating Sachsenhausen, direction northwest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We passed through the Mecklenburg Forest northwest of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On the road, we met columns of women.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was surprised how the women behaved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Among our men groups, people collapsed, break mentally, break physically.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
